lar medium is\nabout 1 MeV, which is also favorable as an explanation of the 511 keV line\nemission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jul 2006 13:42:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 Sep 2006 13:59:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
