rain size. Mean grain size from the inversion shows 90\\% agreement\nwith the ground truth and may be a useful tool for high-frequency acoustic\nsediment classification in shallow water.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jul 2006 19:20:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
